WEBVTT

00:11.010 --> 00:14.431
KIRINOSHIMA MIDDLE SCHOOL

00:16.808 --> 00:18.393
Hey, hey, Koyuki.

00:22.355 --> 00:26.276
Hey, who among us is the hottest?

00:26.359 --> 00:27.360
Huh?

00:30.447 --> 00:32.073
You're adorable!

00:32.574 --> 00:35.827
Knock it off, Tatsu. She's flustered.

00:36.661 --> 00:40.915
Don't bother
with their annoying crap, all right?

00:40.999 --> 00:42.167
Okay.

00:44.335 --> 00:45.462
That's sweet!

00:46.337 --> 00:48.298
Sorry, Koyuki.

00:48.381 --> 00:50.592
You're so tiny,
I didn't even see you there.

00:52.635 --> 00:55.805
Hey, Amano, give her some of your height.

00:57.182 --> 00:58.850
He's so obvious.

00:58.933 --> 01:01.436
- It's plain to see.
- Seriously.

01:03.229 --> 01:04.397
Shorty! Shorty!

01:04.481 --> 01:05.982
Wait, Tiny!

01:07.358 --> 01:09.194
Come on, it's just a joke.

01:09.903 --> 01:11.905
I've been thinking this for a long time.

01:11.988 --> 01:15.492
Igarashi totally has
a crush on you, Koyuki!

01:15.575 --> 01:18.661
Even Tatsu's into you, Koyuki.

01:18.745 --> 01:20.246
I'm jealous.

01:20.747 --> 01:24.042
Why is teasing acceptable
when it's a joke or well-meant?

01:35.470 --> 01:38.223
Tell me. What about my feelings?

01:46.397 --> 01:48.024
MEITEN HIGH SCHOOL

01:48.107 --> 01:50.568
Mari, Muko, and Mei.

01:52.362 --> 01:54.739
Okay, everyone's coming.

01:54.823 --> 01:57.742
We'll throw a snack party
on the last day of the finals!

01:57.826 --> 01:59.410
Woo-hoo!

02:00.203 --> 02:01.329
What should we get?

02:01.412 --> 02:02.747
What sounds good?

02:02.831 --> 02:04.415
Class 5 is so lucky.

02:04.999 --> 02:07.043
Azumi's a literal goddess.

02:07.127 --> 02:10.922
She even greets nerdy introverts like us.
She's heaven-sent.

02:12.674 --> 02:13.675
Hey.

02:14.175 --> 02:15.260
- Huh?
- Huh?

02:18.263 --> 02:19.264
Here.

02:20.723 --> 02:24.435
The teacher wanted me to give it to you.

02:28.148 --> 02:30.567
Thank you very much.

02:34.445 --> 02:35.947
- Scary.
- Scary.

02:36.573 --> 02:37.782
Who was she?

02:37.866 --> 02:39.409
She's Koyuki Hikawa.

02:39.492 --> 02:40.994
People call her "the Queen."

02:41.077 --> 02:42.412
"The Queen"?

02:42.495 --> 02:44.497
She doesn't hang out
with anyone in the class.

02:44.581 --> 02:46.332
That was my first interaction
with her ever.

02:46.416 --> 02:47.959
But the second semester's almost over.

02:48.042 --> 02:50.962
I mean, she's always in a bad mood.

02:51.045 --> 02:53.423
She gives off a "don't come near me" vibe.

02:58.052 --> 03:00.889
Miki, when you make the call,
everyone joins in.

03:00.972 --> 03:02.223
It's not like that.

03:02.307 --> 03:04.225
As expected from Class 5's idol.

03:04.809 --> 03:06.603
Oh, stop.

03:33.755 --> 03:35.256
Winter is already here.

03:36.090 --> 03:38.885
The second semester is coming to a close.

03:39.719 --> 03:42.597
Once the third semester ends,
so will the first year of my high school.

03:44.140 --> 03:47.560
Without anything really happening.

03:51.189 --> 03:54.442
Still, this is far better
than middle school.

03:59.530 --> 04:02.825
It's not that I care
how people see me at this point,

04:03.326 --> 04:05.870
but it still bothered me
when he made that face.

04:06.537 --> 04:09.499
What do they find so scary about me?

04:10.458 --> 04:11.459
Is it my face?

04:13.920 --> 04:15.296
My facial muscles...

04:17.674 --> 04:18.716
Huh?

04:28.226 --> 04:29.602
My bad, my bad.

04:30.311 --> 04:32.063
I was curious what you were doing.

04:32.689 --> 04:34.941
What are you doing, Minato?

04:35.024 --> 04:36.276
Hey, Yota.

04:37.026 --> 04:38.194
Hey!

04:38.278 --> 04:41.155
Why are you picking on a girl?
You're the worst.

04:41.239 --> 04:42.365
It's not like that.

04:42.949 --> 04:45.076
You good? Can you stand up?

04:46.786 --> 04:47.787
Thanks.

04:48.288 --> 04:49.330
Wait.

04:53.918 --> 04:54.919
He's massive!

04:56.713 --> 05:00.258
Sorry about this little rascal
causing you trouble.

05:00.341 --> 05:02.510
I said I didn't do anything.

05:02.593 --> 05:04.262
Is that right?

05:04.345 --> 05:06.764
What do you think I am?

05:07.557 --> 05:10.518
Hikawa, I thought you were more reserved,

05:11.019 --> 05:13.771
- but you can make some funny faces.
- What?

05:13.855 --> 05:15.940
Sorry I startled you.

05:17.817 --> 05:19.110
Well, see you later.

05:27.327 --> 05:28.369
My name...

05:28.453 --> 05:29.454
How...

05:30.038 --> 05:32.332
Who was he, anyway?

07:03.506 --> 07:07.927
EPISODE 1
LINES AND WALLS

07:08.970 --> 07:12.598
I saw this on a live stream yesterday.
Did you know it's gone viral?

07:12.682 --> 07:13.975
I had no idea.

07:14.058 --> 07:15.393
She totally took my seat.

07:15.476 --> 07:16.602
It's at convenience stores.

07:16.686 --> 07:17.687
KOYUKI'S DESK

07:17.770 --> 07:18.771
KOYUKI'S SCALE

07:18.855 --> 07:20.773
EFFORT TO SPEAK UP
EFFORT TO WAIT IT OUT

07:20.857 --> 07:21.858
THUMP

07:21.941 --> 07:23.443
It's fine. I can wait.

07:31.367 --> 07:33.703
Sorry, you want your desk back, right?
I'll move.

07:33.786 --> 07:35.121
GRADE 1 CLASS 2

07:35.788 --> 07:36.998
You don't have to.

07:39.125 --> 07:40.960
AWKWARD VIBE

07:44.046 --> 07:46.466
Say, Hikawa, I'm really sorry.

07:46.549 --> 07:47.550
Huh?

07:48.968 --> 07:50.052
For what?

07:53.222 --> 07:55.850
Did she do something
she needs to apologize for?

08:04.901 --> 08:05.902
MIKI

08:05.985 --> 08:07.320
Have you left already, Koyun?

08:08.863 --> 08:09.864
Not yet.

08:09.947 --> 08:11.199
I'm still at the entrance.

08:11.699 --> 08:13.826
I don't have work today.
Let's walk home together.

08:14.327 --> 08:15.620
Woo-hoo!

08:15.703 --> 08:16.996
Okey froggy!

08:17.079 --> 08:18.331
I'll wait for you out front.

08:18.414 --> 08:19.415
I'll be there soon.

08:20.041 --> 08:22.543
Ten, nine, eight...

08:22.627 --> 08:23.628
Huh? Countdown?

08:23.711 --> 08:24.837
- ...seven...
- Hey!

08:24.921 --> 08:26.130
Wait up!

08:32.053 --> 08:33.971
...six, five,

08:34.055 --> 08:35.973
four, three,

08:36.057 --> 08:37.475
two,

08:37.558 --> 08:38.601
one...

08:38.684 --> 08:39.810
Koyun!

08:49.904 --> 08:51.322
I made it!

08:55.826 --> 08:58.079
Was that funny? Was it?

08:58.162 --> 09:00.581
Who takes it that seriously?

09:00.665 --> 09:02.124
Right? I'm amazing, huh?

09:02.208 --> 09:04.293
That was my best record for the day.

09:06.504 --> 09:08.798
You're such a dummy.

09:10.758 --> 09:12.510
Can I come over after I swing by my place?

09:13.094 --> 09:15.304
Yeah. My mom's not home anyway.

09:15.388 --> 09:19.016
Hold on! You ignored me when
we passed by in the hallway yesterday!

09:19.600 --> 09:23.020
I mean, there was nothing
I wanted to talk about.

09:23.104 --> 09:25.106
That's what I mean!

09:25.773 --> 09:27.275
Look at Azumi go.

09:27.858 --> 09:30.695
Her social skills must be crazy,
pushing the Queen around.

09:34.615 --> 09:35.616
201 - HIKAWA
401 - AZUMI

09:35.700 --> 09:37.535
They're all good girls.

09:38.119 --> 09:40.288
I like them and all, but...

09:40.913 --> 09:44.041
I'm like, what?
People treat me like an idol!

09:44.834 --> 09:47.837
They think I'm a saint or something.

09:49.046 --> 09:50.047
How come?

09:50.131 --> 09:52.425
People oughta treat me like a gorilla,
like they used to!

09:52.508 --> 09:53.801
READ BEAN SOUP - STEEL CAN

09:53.884 --> 09:56.554
Insult me more!

09:57.138 --> 09:59.890
Honestly speaking, I wanna joke around,
get up to dumb things,

09:59.974 --> 10:01.934
and make everyone laugh every day!

10:02.018 --> 10:05.688
I want to make the audience go wild!

10:07.148 --> 10:10.610
You should act like this
in front of your classmates.

10:11.110 --> 10:12.445
Be yourself.

10:12.528 --> 10:15.698
It's not like I'm not being myself, but...

10:16.198 --> 10:17.742
How do I put it?

10:17.825 --> 10:21.954
Even if I want to, I can't switch
to being myself immediately.

10:22.622 --> 10:25.625
Before I know it,
I'm in that mode in that classroom.

10:25.708 --> 10:29.545
It's like who I really am
never even existed.

10:29.629 --> 10:30.713
Actually,

10:32.256 --> 10:34.425
what's the real me?

10:35.134 --> 10:37.470
I don't know what I'm feeling anymore.

10:41.807 --> 10:44.352
Mi... ki?

10:45.936 --> 10:48.856
Crap, crap, crap!
I just got super poetic now.

10:48.939 --> 10:52.818
No, no, no!
That was definitely not the real me!

10:54.612 --> 10:55.821
You'll be fine.

10:56.906 --> 10:59.116
Whether you're an idol or a gorilla,

10:59.200 --> 11:01.327
some people will want to stick by you.

11:02.495 --> 11:06.374
People who weren't meant for you won't,
but there's nothing wrong with that.

11:06.916 --> 11:08.459
Koyun...

11:08.542 --> 11:09.710
Me,

11:10.961 --> 11:15.341
I prefer to be alone
than be around people I don't vibe with.

11:16.676 --> 11:18.886
You're fine not talking to anyone all day?

11:18.969 --> 11:19.970
I'd die!

11:20.054 --> 11:21.680
Yep, that's how you are.

11:22.181 --> 11:26.352
I want the strength
to be alone like you, Koyun.

11:27.061 --> 11:30.856
I'm not saying I'm right.

11:31.524 --> 11:34.777
Someone who can put others ahead
of themselves is wonderful.

11:37.530 --> 11:39.615
But if you're suffering, you should stop.

11:42.201 --> 11:44.120
Even someone as social as Miki

11:44.703 --> 11:49.291
thinks they are different
from how others see them.

11:50.459 --> 11:53.796
It's no good!
All this thinking's going nowhere.

11:53.879 --> 11:55.756
Let's get our exam prep underway.

11:56.507 --> 11:58.259
Yeah, that's a good idea.

11:58.342 --> 12:01.554
To start, tell me
what's covered on the English exam.

12:02.763 --> 12:03.764
We're starting there?

12:12.148 --> 12:15.025
I love the classroom early in the morning.

12:15.901 --> 12:18.028
Vocabulary book, vocabulary book...

12:20.364 --> 12:21.740
GRADE 1 CLASS 5 NUMBER 1
MIKI AZUMI

12:21.824 --> 12:23.284
This is Miki's.

12:24.952 --> 12:27.621
That's right, we studied together
at my place yesterday.

12:28.664 --> 12:31.333
She'll probably need it for her class.
I have to give it back to her.

12:32.209 --> 12:33.210
GRADE 1 CLASS 5

12:33.294 --> 12:36.881
I bet Miki's not even at school yet.
I'll leave it in her desk.

12:40.217 --> 12:41.385
Huh?

12:47.516 --> 12:48.559
Huh?

12:49.560 --> 12:50.561
What?

12:59.153 --> 13:00.613
I got you.

13:01.113 --> 13:03.407
That surprised me!

13:04.033 --> 13:05.159
Are you okay?

13:05.826 --> 13:08.245
It's the guy from the other day.

13:09.497 --> 13:10.789
Huh?

13:10.873 --> 13:13.918
Huh? What? Wait, wait, wait, wait!

13:14.835 --> 13:18.464
What on earth is happening?

13:20.966 --> 13:23.719
Koyuki, feed Mr. Giraffe.

13:34.522 --> 13:36.607
You're the girl from before.

13:37.149 --> 13:38.150
Yeah.

13:38.234 --> 13:42.071
I don't have my contacts in today.
I couldn't tell it was you.

13:42.154 --> 13:44.657
Sorry I bumped into you. Are you okay?

13:48.202 --> 13:50.871
I had a flashback just now.

13:51.580 --> 13:52.623
What's this?

13:56.001 --> 13:57.253
Are you a friend of Miki's?

13:58.587 --> 13:59.630
Yes.

14:00.464 --> 14:01.465
Miki?

14:01.966 --> 14:03.926
Might you be in Class 5?

14:04.635 --> 14:06.595
Nope. I'm in Class 6.

14:06.679 --> 14:10.391
I came to grab a textbook
I lent to a friend.

14:11.100 --> 14:12.893
- Here.
- Thank you.

14:13.644 --> 14:16.272
I'm here to return this to Miki.

14:19.441 --> 14:23.153
- I don't know where she sits.
- Are you serious?

14:24.488 --> 14:27.074
Let's see. This should be her desk.

14:27.157 --> 14:29.910
- Should?
- I'm kidding. It definitely is.

14:30.578 --> 14:32.621
Wanna scribble a message on her desk?

14:33.122 --> 14:35.291
Something like, "I brought your notebook."

14:35.374 --> 14:37.543
It's fine. I'll send her a message.

14:38.252 --> 14:40.129
That's one way to go.

14:40.212 --> 14:42.548
I wrote a ton on my friend's desk.

14:43.132 --> 14:45.467
Like, "I grabbed my textbook."

14:47.720 --> 14:50.431
He seems like a mellow guy.

14:50.973 --> 14:52.099
See you.

14:52.683 --> 14:54.518
Thank you.

14:54.602 --> 14:56.729
Let's ace the exam.

15:00.149 --> 15:01.525
Himuro.

15:02.902 --> 15:05.279
Himuro isn't my name.

15:05.362 --> 15:06.530
HIKAWA

15:07.239 --> 15:11.118
Oh, well.
We hardly ever run into each other anyway.

15:23.797 --> 15:24.965
Peaceful.

15:25.049 --> 15:26.050
Quiet.

15:26.717 --> 15:27.927
That's enough for me.

15:32.348 --> 15:35.935
Why do men like to hang out in groups?

15:36.602 --> 15:38.103
Well, I guess it depends on the person.

15:39.688 --> 15:44.068
He was with the person
who's like a giraffe.

15:45.194 --> 15:46.278
They're in the same grade.

15:46.362 --> 15:47.363
GRADE 1 - GRADE 2 - GRADE 3

15:47.446 --> 15:48.614
THE SLIPPER COLOR IS DIFFERENT
BY GRADE

15:49.573 --> 15:52.368
I've tried not to pay attention
to my surroundings until now.

15:52.993 --> 15:57.790
Things like who's in my grade
never mattered to me.

16:03.003 --> 16:04.004
Crap.

16:04.088 --> 16:05.464
We made eye contact...

16:05.547 --> 16:07.257
I think? Maybe?

16:10.678 --> 16:14.139
I looked away without thinking.
It was kind of awkward.

16:14.640 --> 16:17.434
But I don't know him well enough
to go say hi.

16:20.437 --> 16:21.772
Oh, well.

16:22.439 --> 16:25.025
Milk tea, or...

16:25.734 --> 16:27.611
Chocolate milk sounds good too.

16:27.695 --> 16:29.029
Definitely pass.

16:29.697 --> 16:30.698
Hey.

16:32.616 --> 16:34.493
Why did you ignore me?

16:35.744 --> 16:37.121
Ignore you?

16:37.204 --> 16:39.289
I waved but you ran away.

16:39.915 --> 16:41.125
Huh? You waved?

16:42.126 --> 16:43.293
What a shock!

16:44.294 --> 16:45.629
I'm sorry.

16:45.713 --> 16:46.839
I guess?

16:47.339 --> 16:49.550
I didn't even notice.

16:49.633 --> 16:51.719
I wasn't trying to be mean.

16:52.302 --> 16:53.554
Yup, I know.

16:54.054 --> 16:55.556
- Huh?
- Your drink.

16:58.142 --> 17:00.310
AUTHENTIC CURRY DRINK

17:00.894 --> 17:02.604
Do you like it?

17:02.688 --> 17:05.065
No, I got the wrong one.

17:05.149 --> 17:08.068
It's totally my fault then. My bad.

17:08.652 --> 17:12.406
He doesn't seem like a bad person, but...

17:13.615 --> 17:16.744
When someone is this different from me...

17:16.827 --> 17:18.162
Heya!

17:18.954 --> 17:22.583
...I can't help but be wary and suspicious.

17:23.667 --> 17:26.170
Besides, who are you anyway?

17:27.337 --> 17:28.422
Hey!

17:29.006 --> 17:30.924
What're you up to, Amamiya?

17:31.842 --> 17:32.926
Amamiya?

17:33.635 --> 17:36.680
That's me. I'm Minato Amamiya.

17:37.264 --> 17:38.515
Good to meet you.

17:39.224 --> 17:40.601
Likewise.

17:40.684 --> 17:42.603
Wait. You're introducing yourself now?

17:42.686 --> 17:43.687
Are you hitting on her?

17:43.771 --> 17:45.105
What's going on?

17:46.273 --> 17:50.027
Isn't he overly friendly?

17:50.110 --> 17:51.820
You've gotta keep your guard up.

17:51.904 --> 17:53.322
Just kidding.

17:53.906 --> 17:55.365
Give it a rest.

17:55.449 --> 17:58.952
- Get back over there. Shoo.
- So that's their vibe.

17:59.036 --> 18:00.037
Gosh.

18:00.537 --> 18:03.332
I really can't stand it.

18:03.916 --> 18:05.084
Huh?

18:11.673 --> 18:13.550
What's he doing out of the blue?

18:15.427 --> 18:18.305
I know what this is. He's teasing me.

18:18.931 --> 18:20.766
MIND THEATER
WHAT TO DO WHEN YOU GET TEASED

18:20.849 --> 18:22.601
What's the correct response?

18:22.684 --> 18:24.311
One, get worked up.

18:25.270 --> 18:26.355
I'm fuming!

18:26.438 --> 18:27.898
Two, act flustered.

18:27.981 --> 18:29.608
Knock it off, hey.

18:30.359 --> 18:31.735
Three, laugh it off.

18:31.819 --> 18:33.278
That's hilarious.

18:34.571 --> 18:35.864
For now...

18:39.993 --> 18:41.870
I'll give him a smile.

18:41.954 --> 18:43.622
Three, laugh it off. Ha ha ha.

18:50.921 --> 18:53.882
My gosh, she creeps me out.

18:53.966 --> 18:58.220
Hold on, did she get mad
because I butted in?

18:58.720 --> 19:00.013
I'm sure that wasn't it.

19:03.392 --> 19:05.185
That felt more like

19:05.811 --> 19:08.272
she put up a wall.

19:18.615 --> 19:21.910
Hey, Amano, give her some of your height.

19:21.994 --> 19:23.370
Okay.

19:24.580 --> 19:26.498
Koyuki.

19:32.754 --> 19:35.924
Koyuki, do you like Igarashi?

19:42.014 --> 19:43.807
Did you see it?

19:43.891 --> 19:45.809
It was so funny.

19:46.310 --> 19:47.436
Seriously.

19:51.523 --> 19:53.942
I'm sorry, Koyuki.

20:05.037 --> 20:06.955
Don't get cocky.

21:58.817 --> 22:00.485
MIKI: I'M SORRY KOYUN!

22:00.569 --> 22:03.447
HR IS GOING ON FOREVER - IT'LL
BE A WHILE BEFORE I CAN LEAVE

22:03.530 --> 22:05.157
YOU KNOW WHERE
THE COMMUNITY CENTER IS?

22:05.240 --> 22:06.491
IF YOU DO, WAIT FOR ME THERE...

22:07.117 --> 22:08.327
I see.

22:09.286 --> 22:11.955
Hey, hey! Are you by yourself?

22:12.039 --> 22:13.081
I'm not.

22:13.165 --> 22:15.834
Whatever! You're funny.

22:15.917 --> 22:17.252
Why is this happening?

22:18.211 --> 22:19.379
Why?

22:19.463 --> 22:22.424
Why do people come onto me
like this when I'm not at school?

22:24.593 --> 22:25.761
Wait up.

22:27.471 --> 22:30.474
It's all right. We don't bite.

22:30.974 --> 22:33.310
Look who's talking.

22:34.478 --> 22:37.105
- I am.
- This kind of vibe.

22:39.983 --> 22:41.610
I really, really can't stand it.

22:42.986 --> 22:44.154
Oh, no.

22:44.738 --> 22:45.864
I have to get away.

22:56.166 --> 22:57.834
What's his name again?

22:58.960 --> 23:00.337
What's this out of the blue?

23:01.004 --> 23:02.005
NOW THINKING

23:04.424 --> 23:06.176
- Hey, what's her deal?
- Maybe she knows him.

23:08.637 --> 23:09.763
He noticed--

23:11.973 --> 23:13.391
His terrible vision!

23:16.728 --> 23:17.938
He left.

23:18.522 --> 23:20.690
He ignored you!

23:21.942 --> 23:23.485
Join us for a good time.

23:23.568 --> 23:24.611
No thanks!

23:25.237 --> 23:26.238
What do I even do?

23:26.321 --> 23:27.656
TWO AGAINST ONE
WHAT IF I UPSET THEM

23:27.739 --> 23:28.740
I'm terrified and angry.

23:28.824 --> 23:30.117
THEY'RE MOCKING ME
WHAT A WASTE OF TIME

23:30.700 --> 23:32.119
- How frustrating...
- Let's go.

23:32.202 --> 23:33.411
- Come with us.
- It's gonna be fun.

23:33.495 --> 23:35.997
I said I'm not interested!

